AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:GENEPIO_0001880 "Some dates don't belong to a range other than the overall timeline.

Other dates associated with a process fall within a range that has a start and end bound."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:GENEPIO_0001880 "datetime linear coordinate"@en)
