AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:GENEPIO_0001889 "The \"Canadia postal code FSA\" is the leading FSA (Forward Sortation Area) 3 character portion of a full 6 character Canadian postal code.  It can be used to reduce the geographic granularity of a postal code for data generalization or obfuscation."@en)
